{"tid":2179815,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"政府豪花258萬落A1廣告硬銷檢測 首日僅22萬人登記 《蘋果》頭版有小店撐","createTime":"2020-08-29T11:40:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T04:32:05.000Z","uid":240362,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f2cff8b948fe160d602a48b4706443b04d3a73e8","tid":2179815,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:40:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/9RCEOoAiuzFGGVWKszRcRYdyaIc=/1440x810/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4XD37N7CP5AETLWPDBL6T62BTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F9RCEOoAiuzFGGVWKszRcRYdyaIc%3D%2F1440x810%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4XD37N7CP5AETLWPDBL6T62BTM.jpg&h=452550d1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n港府今（29日）於多份中文報章登頭版廣告，呼籲市民參與檢測，包括《明報》、《星島》、《東方》等，唯獨《蘋果》除外，《蘋果》今日頭版則繼續有小店力撐，超過60間小店落聯合廣告，推廣「connect card project」，並寫上「Ｗe Stand We Connect」，部份商戶並在小格寫有「與蘋果撐自由」、「撐住呀香港人」、「歡迎689share」等字句。<br />\n<br />\n政府發言人回覆查詢表示，政府今日在本港11份中英文報章的頭版及內頁，刊登有關廣告，涉及開支約258萬元。截至傍晚近6時，全民檢測首日有22萬人已登記。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/B23LHXHVRRDYZKGWNZD2YGX7G4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FB23LHXHVRRDYZKGWNZD2YGX7G4%2F&d=aJB%2Bq6ruafnyRbkwc%2FW5Zris81FSeaDeH2Oz4vdBzj8%3D&h=f1a8ea58\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200829%2FB23LHXHVRRDYZKGWNZD2YGX7G4%2F&h=0db76e02\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200829/B23LHXHVRRDYZKGWNZD2YGX7G4/</a>"},{"pid":"8c90e5960bc78e7abd375ba90e8f9bba198453b6","tid":2179815,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-29T11:42:19.000Z","msg":"我愛蘋果<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4973979b3594f061f06291fbe3362242caab8100","tid":2179815,"